summary: " You are in love with him." was the first thing Rhodey said, after Doctor Strange left. Tony blinked in suprise and confusion....
body:
“ You are in love with him.” was the first thing Rhodey said, after Doctor Strange left. Tony blinked in suprise and confusion. “What?” “Aw,come on Tones! I saw the way you looked at him,although I knew it already as he entered the room,because you lighted up like a freaking Chrismas tree.” explained Rhodey with a knowing smirk. Tony blushed a little bit. “Am I really so obvious? That’s kinda embarrassing.” he thought. “Don`t worry he feels the same way” insured Rhodey.

“You really like Tony Stark, don’t you?” Wong asked as Stephen sat down. The Sorcerer didn’t looked at him as he answerd:“I don’t know what you mean.” “I mean you are ridiculous in love wiht this man.” replied the older one simply. A little shocked and embarrasssed Strange looked up:“How do you…” “Oh come on, you two a quite obvious.”


A little thing I wrote to practice writing in english. Maybe some of you like it.
